metadata.name: Skorts - Muyu Tanaka
metadata.description:
The " Skorts " series is the first NFT mini-series in the SMBEG collection of the " Sailor Moan become Eth Girl" R18 comics
This series has the theme of Main Character's SMBEG wearing tennis clothes with a touch of fantasy, "crystal" balloons which are symbols of my previous works at the foundation. I love to color the sky blue which reminds me of freedom, serenity, and fun!



the collector will receive a .jpeg file + airdropped the collector's gift which includes unlockable content ( SMBEG's Comics R18 CENSORED Chapter Prologue
